cs.LO, cs.AI, cs.PL, cs.LG, cs.MS 

The paper involves formalizing and automating a philosophical argument using automated theorem provers, which suggests it could belong to the category of Logic in Computer Science (cs.LO). Additionally, the use of automated theorem provers suggests it could also belong to the categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Programming Languages (cs.PL). The paper also offers a novel perspective towards a computational theoretical philosophy, which could place it in the categories of Machine Learning (cs.LG) or Mathematical Software (cs.MS).
